1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Kitten Economics Episode 5: Incentives.

2
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Welcome back. Today we learn one core economics idea with kittens.

3
00:00:45,000 --> 00:01:15,000
At home, Coco the kitten ignores cleanup time.

4
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:45,000
Then the rule changes: every toy returned to the basket earns one tiny fish sticker. Behavior changes immediately.

5
00:01:45,000 --> 00:02:10,000
Incentives shape choices. Good incentives make the desired action easier and rewarding; bad incentives create shortcuts and gaming.

6
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:35,000
Recap: Incentives. Use this rule in real decisions. Comment: More Kitten Economics.
